        "children": [
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "As much as Stellantis hates it, the fact is thieves really focus on high-end Mopars for a quick score. That fact was recently highlighted by a long-term investigative report by Channel 7 in Detroit, a city where car thefts in general are out of control. For 2021, vehicle theft surged 24% from 5,578 cars stolen in 2020 to 6,939 for 2021.",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          }
        ],
        "direction": "ltr",
